    "text": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>2-5-160</b>\n</p><p>Group-flashing light in which the flashes are combined in successive groups of different num-bers of flashes. (Fig. 40d)\n</p><p><span class=\"mw-image-border\" typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:Ch2_Fig40.jpg\" class=\"mw-file-description\"><img src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/3/30/Ch2_Fig40.jpg/100px-Ch2_Fig40.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"100\" height=\"52\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/3/30/Ch2_Fig40.jpg/150px-Ch2_Fig40.jpg 1.5x, /wiki/dictionary/images/thumb/3/30/Ch2_Fig40.jpg/200px-Ch2_Fig40.jpg 2x\"></a></span>\n</p><p>Reference: <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"8d9c307cb7f3c4a32822a51922d1ceaa\">N</span>.<span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"d20caec3b48a1eef164cb4ca81ba2587\">L</span>. (modified)\n</p><p><br>\n<br>\n<br>\n<i>Please note that this is the term as it stands in the original <span class=\"mw-lingo-term\" data-lingo-term-id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\">IALA</span> Dictionary edition (1970-1989)</i>\n<br>\n</p>\n<div class=\"LanguageLinks\">\n<table width=\"100%\">\n<tbody><tr valign=\"top\" style=\"background: #FFFFFF\">\n<td style=\"width: 25px; padding-left: 0em; border-right: 1px solid #aaaaaa;border-left: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-top: 1px solid #EEF3E2;border-bottom: 1px solid #EEF3E2;\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/dictionary/index.php/File:25px-Geographylogo.png\" class=\"mw-file-description\" title=\"Languages\"><img alt=\"Languages\" src=\"/wiki/dictionary/images/8/82/25px-Geographylogo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"25\" height=\"25\" class=\"mw-file-element\"></a></span></td>\n<td style=\"padding: 1px 1em 0; background: #EEF3E2;\">\n<p><b><a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">English</a></b>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n<span></span>\n</p>\n</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"8d9c307cb7f3c4a32822a51922d1ceaa\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>North\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>No\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Newton\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Julian date\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"d20caec3b48a1eef164cb4ca81ba2587\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Luminance\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Level (technician training - WWA)\n</p>\n</div></div><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>Latitude (in degrees)\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div><div class=\"mw-lingo-tooltip\" id=\"0a1217bfe27a54fc7e55b72fc62c2371\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition navigation-not-searchable\"><div class=\"mw-lingo-definition-text\">\n<p>International Association of Marine Aids to Navigation and Lighthouse Authorities - AISM\n</p>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260615015850\nCache expiry: 86400\nReduced expiry: false\nComplications: []\nCPU time usage: 0.045 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.057 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 60/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 851/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 398/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/100\nExpensive parser function count: 4/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   17.894      1 -total\n 74.19%   13.275      1 Template:Langua